She stopped by a closed door in the hallway.  She thought she heard 
something behind it for a moment.  She leaned her ear against the door and 
listened.  She heard nothing on the other side.  She started walking again 
down the hallway. Two more doors down and I'm back with my commanders, she 
thought.
